<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EC) No 660/1999 of 22 March 1999 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2075/92 and fixing the premiums and guarantee thresholds for leaf tobacco by variety group and Member State for the 1999, 2000 and 2001 harvests </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 660/1999, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2075/92 ja m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks lehttubaka tagatisk&uuml;nnised tubakasortide r&uuml;hmade ja liikmesriikide j&auml;rgi 1999., 2000. ja 2001. aasta saakide puhul 22. m&auml;rts 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA LIIDU N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, and in particular Articles 42 and 43 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artikleid 42 ja 43, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2075/92 of 30 June 1992 on the common organisation of the market in raw tobacco (1), and in particular Articles 4(1), 8 and 9(2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2075/92 toortubakaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) eriti selle artikli 4 l&otilde;iget 1, artiklit 8 ja artikli 9 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament (3), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi arvamust, (3) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the Economic and Social Committee (4), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse majandus- ja sotsiaalkomitee arvamust (4) ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas a supplementary amount is granted for flue-cured, light air-cured and dark air-cured tobaccos grown in Austria, Belgium, France and Germany; whereas the Council decided to raise that amount from 50 % to 65 % of the difference on the basis of the 1992 harvest; whereas this increase is to be calculated on the basis of the difference between the premium granted for those tobaccos for the 1998 harvest and the premium applicable to the 1992 harvest; whereas Article 3(2) of Regulation (EEC) No 2075/92 is not consistent with this; whereas Article 3(2) of Regulation (EEC) No 2075/92 should therefore be amended; </inglise>
<eesti> Austrias, Belgias, Prantsusmaal ja Saksamaal kasvatatud suitsus kuivatatud, &otilde;hu k&auml;es kuivatatud heleda ja &otilde;hu k&auml;es kuivatatud tumeda tubaka puhul makstakse siiski t&auml;iendav summa; n&otilde;ukogu otsustas nimetatud summat t&otilde;sta 50 protsendilt 65 protsendile, v&otilde;ttes aluseks 1992. aasta saagi erinevuse; see suurendamine arvutatakse nende tubakate 1998. aasta saagi suhtes makstud lisatasu ja 1992. aasta saagikoristuse suhtes kohaldatava lisatasu erinevuse p&otilde;hjal; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2075/92 artikli 3 l&otilde;ige 2 ei ole sellega koosk&otilde;las; seet&otilde;ttu on vaja muuta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2075/92 artikli 3 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the level of premiums should be fixed having regard to the objectives of the common agricultural policy and in particular to ensure a fair standard of living for the farming community; whereas the premium amounts should reflect past and foreseeable market outlets for the various tobaccos under normal conditions of competition; whereas the level of the premiums should be fixed for three consecutive harvests and be linked to the guarantee thresholds established for the three harvests in 1999, 2000 and 2001 in order to ensure that the stability of the sector is maintained; </inglise>
<eesti> lisatasude m&auml;&auml;r tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika eesm&auml;rke ning arvesse v&otilde;ttes eelk&otilde;ige selleks, et tagada p&otilde;llumeestele rahuldav elatustase; lisatasude summad peaksid kajastama erinevate tubakasortide seniseid ja prognoositavaid turustusv&otilde;imalusi tavalistel konkurentsitingimustel; sektori stabiilsuse s&auml;ilitamiseks tuleks lisatasude m&auml;&auml;r kinnitada kolme j&auml;rjestikuse saagi jaoks ja see peaks olema seotud 1999., 2000. ja 2001. aasta saakidele kehtestatud tagatisk&uuml;nnistega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the second paragraph of Article 8 and Article 9(2) of Regulation (EEC) No 2075/92 provide for the allocation among producer Member States of guarantee thresholds for each variety group for three harvests as from the 1999 harvest; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2075/92 artikli 8 teise l&otilde;igu ja artikli 9 l&otilde;ikega 2 n&auml;hakse ette 1999. aasta saagikoristusest alates tagatisk&uuml;nniste jagamine tootjaliikmesriikide vahel k&otilde;ikide sordir&uuml;hmade puhul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the level of those thresholds for the three harvests in 1999, 2000 and 2001 should be fixed having regard, in particular, to market conditions and socio-economic and agricultural conditions obtaining in the production zones concerned; whereas such fixing should be done in good time to allow producers to plan their production for the said harvests; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealuste k&uuml;nniste tase 1999., 2000. ja 2001. aasta saakide puhul, v&otilde;ttes eriti arvesse asjaomaste tootmispiirkondade turutingimusi ning sotsiaalmajanduslikke ja p&otilde;llumajanduslikke tingimusi; selline kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramine peaks toimuma aegsasti, et tootjatel oleks v&otilde;imalik kavandada tootmist eespool nimetatud saakide osas; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, as a result of the increase in supplementary amounts for flue-cured, light air-cured and dark air-cured tobaccos grown in Austria, Belgium, France and Germany, the guarantee thresholds of these Member States should be reduced in order to ensure the maintenance of budget neutrality; </inglise>
<eesti> Austrias, Belgias, Prantsusmaal ja Saksamaal kasvatatud suitsus kuivatatud, &otilde;hu k&auml;es kuivatatud heleda ja &otilde;hu k&auml;es kuivatatud tumeda tubaka puhul t&auml;iendavate summade suurendamise t&otilde;ttu tuleks nimetatud liikmesriikide tagatisk&uuml;nniseid v&auml;hendada, et tagada eelarveneutraliteedi s&auml;ilimine; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, while maintaining production potential and the allocation of quotas by Member States, quotas for varieties which have assured outlets and attract high market prices should be increased progressively to the detriment of quotas for varieties which are difficult to sell and attract low market prices; </inglise>
<eesti> tootmisv&otilde;imsuse s&auml;ilitamise ja liikmesriikide poolt kvootide eraldamise k&otilde;rval tuleks nende sortide kvoote, mille puhul on tagatud turustusv&otilde;imalused ja millel on k&otilde;rge turuhind, j&auml;rk-j&auml;rgult suurendada nende sortide kvootide arvelt, mida on raske m&uuml;&uuml;a ja millel on madalad turuhinnad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures in question should be introduced as soon as possible, </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealused meetmed tuleks v&otilde;imalikult kiiresti rakendada; </eesti>
